or":{"id":"4f2fb9415a58465f5a562f61ae408c33","url_token":"wu-zhi-de-zha-zha-hui","name":"遛狗的跛脚猫","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-e543e06d4d43a9804835e6f01b6f43c2_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-e543e06d4d43a9804835e6f01b6f43c2_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/4f2fb9415a58465f5a562f61ae408c33","user_type":"people","headline":"白日醉酒，也能梦压星河","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561339715","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545960338,"updated_time":1545960338,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e很多人无法理解为什么问题下满是嘲讽\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这么说吧\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e在知乎直接骂人被举报是会被封号的\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e所以题主还是考虑周全啊\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e另：加油哦题主，希望你用实力打死数学研究者们，或者，被他们打死。这个不算嘲讽吧，世界就是这样，想被关注还没有应有的水平，这才是不公平8\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561329363,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"fd1ea1b42b0acc44f793ab9b6c0a041e","url_token":"pang-ya-lu-4","name":"一头迷鹿","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-2281a36ca85abcfc279b017d4544b267_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-2281a36ca85abcfc279b017d4544b267_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/fd1ea1b42b0acc44f793ab9b6c0a041e","user_type":"people","headline":"医学生/有女朋友","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561329363","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545959466,"updated_time":1545959466,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e说实话 能证明出来我的确佩服 \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是 几乎每个回答下面都有你的一句1月1发表\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我就觉得有种哗众取宠的感觉\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不管最后你的证明是不是正确的\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e看现在的局势 等着看你笑话的人貌似更多\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e当然我不否认 我也是其中一个\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e等你的证明被否决 你的高中很可能将全部浪费在“上次的错误只是意外 我错的不离谱 我还能补救 我还想拥有更大的成就”上\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e然后得不到前面回答里所说的去全球知名大学教书的成就\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e也错失了高考前好好学习的机会\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e（当然我要是被打脸了 我也会为你高兴）\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561326006,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"3e0c73e98dc1e98cbb8d690ad4feef29","url_token":"wang-ting-zhen-15","name":"Anothercrop","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-106a1af7ed9f9ce60905896426338204_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-106a1af7ed9f9ce60905896426338204_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/3e0c73e98dc1e98cbb8d690ad4feef29","user_type":"people","headline":"南开大学本科生","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561326006","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545959164,"updated_time":1545978180,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e曾经我也自以为成功尺规三等分角\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e现在学了群论对尺规无法三等分角的证明深信不疑\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果题主真心有志于数学研究可以考虑下应用更广的黎曼猜想和能让成千上万人下岗的p=np问题嘛，不过我高中的时候在网上搜千禧大奖难题看得懂的好像只有哥德巴赫猜想。还好我高中时候没有手机也不知道知乎哈哈\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561307911,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://w