。来知乎问其实答友也给不了你什么确切答案，多数就是来看好戏和冷嘲热讽。不知道说什么，只能说这些，也不想冷嘲热讽，打击你……毕竟难得有兴趣。但是你真不该来知乎提这类问题……因为这个知友也帮不了你什么。还会觉得你傻。因为提这类问题的人年年有，但真正会的人极少。大多数人不会乱相信。另外假如像评论说的难度极大，那么……emmmmmm，只能说有兴趣是好的……（我也不想总像别人那样纯粹打击他，毕竟还只是个高中学生。）还有，妈蛋这个怎么会有这么多评论……不管怎么样这类问题忽视不好吗？？？？？还有些人等着出主意……\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561263438,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561263438","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545936515,"updated_time":1545936515,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e关于哥德巴赫猜想，我有个绝妙的证明方法，可是知乎回答区太小，写不下。说到写不下，我就想起吴承恩写西游记，今年下半年，中美联机合拍的西游记即将上映，届时我将继续担任美猴王的角色，希望大家多多关注，文体两开花。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561182548,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"6223d66a7b7644b42ba3ddb523453e39","url_token":"lqcgreat","name":"小林桑","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-8a32161a30c2e8362605bf8006c9030d_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-8a32161a30c2e8362605bf8006c9030d_{size}.jp